        WHERE [r].[ReportId] = @__reportId_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[WaterDeptEmail]
    FROM [County] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__countyId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [City] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[CountyId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
